<subSubSection type="nomenclature">
<paragraph>
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:138803" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Ponera" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Ponera antipodum Forel" lsidName-HNS="Ponera antipodum Forel" order="Hymenoptera" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="antipodum">Ponera antipodum</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel rank="species">nov. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection type="description">
<paragraph>
- [[ worker ]]. L. 3, 4 mill. Mandibules armees de six dents assez indistinctes. Tete distinctement plus large derriere que devant. Le sillon frontal assez faible derriere (devant l'ocelle anterieur). Oeil plus distant du bord anterieur de la tete que la moitie de sa largeur (moins distant que le tiers de sa largeur chez la 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:138892" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Ponera" genus.outerRound="1" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Ponera punctatissima Roger" lsidName-HNS="Ponera punctatissima Roger" order="Hymenoptera" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctatissima">P. punctatissima</taxonomicName>
[[ worker ]]). Ecaille un peu plus mince que chez la 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:138892" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Ponera" genus.outerRound="1" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Ponera punctatissima Roger" lsidName-HNS="Ponera punctatissima Roger" order="Hymenoptera" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctatissima">P. punctatissima</taxonomicName>
; chacun des deux premiers segments de l'abdomen est presque aussi long ou aussi long que large. Noire; pattes, antennes et mandibules d'un roux jaunatre; massue des antennes et milieu des scapes bruns. Du reste identique a la 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:138892" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Ponera" genus.outerRound="1" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Ponera punctatissima Roger" lsidName-HNS="Ponera punctatissima Roger" order="Hymenoptera" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctatissima">P. punctatissima</taxonomicName>
[[ worker ]], dont elle est difficile a distinguer.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection type="materials_examined">
<paragraph>
Voisine aussi de la 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:228145" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Ponera" genus.outerRound="1" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Ponera punctatissima var. trigona Mayr" lsidName-HNS="Ponera punctatissima var. trigona Mayr" order="Hymenoptera" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="trigona">P. trigona Mayr</taxonomicName>
. - Rotorua (Nouvelle-Zelande), recoltee par le capitaine Broun.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
